'''貝特希·阿德斯馬'''（1947年7月11日－1969年11月28日）是美國[[宾夕法尼亚州立大学|宾夕法尼亚州立大学]]的學生，她於1969年11月28日在大學圖書館「派蒂圖書館」（Pattee Library）遇害。至今，此案仍未能偵破。

==背景==
死者貝特希出生於[[密歇根州|密芝根州]]{{link-en|賀蘭市|Holland, Michigan}}，是家中的次女<ref name=anthony>{{cite news|last=Anthony|first=Ted|title=Penn State murder a mystery 20 years later|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1144&dat=19891126&id=jIMcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=mmMEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6902,6122527|accessdate=April 29, 2014|newspaper=The Pittsburgh Press|page=A14|date=June 23, 1957}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=A decades-old mystery: The murder of Betsy Aardsma|url=https://www.pennlive.com/specialprojects/2008/12/they_are_old_men_now.html|accessdate=2019-07-06|date=2008-12-07|last=Patriot-News|first=The|work=pennlive.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626035726/https://www.pennlive.com/specialprojects/2008/12/they_are_old_men_now.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她於賀蘭高中畢業後來到[[密芝根大學|密芝根大學]]攻讀藝術和英文。之後，在完成學業後她又到賓夕凡尼亞州立大學當[[研究生|研究生]]。在她遇害的那年，她與一名叫大衛·賴特的醫科生「非正式地訂婚」<ref name=pittsburgh>{{cite news|title=Penn State Girl's Death Probed|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1144&dat=19691129&id=e80bAAAAIBAJ&sjid=WlAEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4922,7095516|accessdate=April 29, 2014|newspaper=The Pittsburgh Press|page=2|date=November 29, 1969}}</ref>。

==遇害==
事發當日為1969年11月28日，貝特希為完成論文而前往派蒂圖書館找資料。在下午4時45分至55分期間，她在到二樓第50排和第51排書架之間遇刺，其左側胸膛被刀刃刺破，直接插穿[[肺動脈|肺動脈]]和[[右心室|右心室]]。鑑於貝特希手部沒有任何因防衛造成的傷痕，警方相信她是被人從後方襲擊<ref>{{Cite web|title=Penn State Cold Case: The Unsolved Murder of Betsy Aardsma|url=https://www.collegemagazine.com/penn-state-cold-case-unsolved-murder-betsy-aardsma/|accessdate=2019-07-06|date=2014-10-31|work=College Magazine|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610113936/https://www.collegemagazine.com/penn-state-cold-case-unsolved-murder-betsy-aardsma/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在被刺後，貝特希隨即臥在地上。一至兩分鐘後，有男子向櫃面職員表示「最好派人去幫幫那女子」後就離開圖書館。然後，在圖書館的人替貝特希進行[[人工呼吸|人工呼吸]]<ref name="Daily Collegian">{{cite news|title=Cries for Help go Unheeded|url=http://digitalnewspapers.libraries.psu.edu/Default/Scripting/ArticleWin.asp?From=Search&Key=DCG/1969/12/02/1/Ar00100.xml&CollName=DCG_APA3&DOCID=54937&PageLabelPrint=1&skin=collegian&AW=1355430482187&AppName=2&sPublication=PFL&sPublication=STC&sPublication=PSC&sPublication=SCG&sPublication=DCG&sQuery=cries%20for%20help%20unheeded&sSorting=%2553%2563%256f%2572%2565%252c%2564%2565%2573%2563&sDateFrom=%2530%2534%252f%2530%2531%252f%2531%2538%2538%2537&sDateTo=%2531%2532%252f%2531%2531%252f%2531%2539%2538%2537&ViewMode=GIF|work=Daily Collegian|date=1969-12-02|accessdate=2012-12-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429203335/http://digitalnewspapers.libraries.psu.edu/Default/Scripting/ArticleWin.asp?From=Search&Key=DCG%2F1969%2F12%2F02%2F1%2FAr00100.xml&CollName=DCG_APA3&DOCID=54937&PageLabelPrint=1&skin=collegian&AW=1355430482187&AppName=2&sPublication=PFL&sPublication=STC&sPublication=PSC&sPublication=SCG&sPublication=DCG&sQuery=cries%20for%20help%20unheeded&sSorting=%2553%2563%256f%2572%2565%252c%2564%2565%2573%2563&sDateFrom=%2530%2534%252f%2530%2531%252f%2531%2538%2538%2537&sDateTo=%2531%2532%252f%2531%2531%252f%2531%2539%2538%2537&ViewMode=GIF|archivedate=2014-04-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 。然而，由於她當時身穿紅色衣服加上只有少量流血，這使得人們看不到她被行刺，而是認為她[[癲癇|癲癇]]發作。直至5時19分，她被送到大學的醫療中心。此時，她才被醫療人員發現其胸膛被刺中，並宣佈她已經離世<ref name=pittsburgh/>。

至2015年11月6日，此案尚未偵破，{{link-en|賓夕凡尼亞州警察局|Pennsylvania State Police}}依積極地收集相關資料<ref name="Chicago Tribune">{{cite news|title=Decades later, Penn State library slaying unsolved|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/chi-ap-pa-psu-libraryslayin,0,1703066.story|work=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|date=2008-08-02|accessdate=2008-08-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611203529/http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/chi-ap-pa-psu-libraryslayin,0,1703066.story|archivedate=2019-06-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

